text: Stade Beaucairois is a French football club based in Beaucaire, Languedoc- Roussillon. It was founded in 1908 as Beaucaire Olympique. The club currently plays in the Championnat National 3. ==External links== * Category:Football clubs in France Category:Association football clubs established in 1908 Category:1908 establishments in France
